<br>
&quot;Predatorus?&quot; she murmured, &quot;Is that you? Have you come to help us again?&quot; <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=594544" target="top"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:gold;font-family:Garamond;font-size:medium;">Saphron LaFeete</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--> <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:purple;font-family:garamond;font-size:small;">High Priestess of Bristlebane </span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#141419><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub148.ezboard.com/bthewordsofnagafen.showUserPublicProfile?gid=sylvrwolf>SylvrWolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>CoN Member</span><br>  Posts: 288<br> <font color=#7A8798>(8/19/03 4:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub148.ezboard.com/fthewordsofnagafenmuirlansweeklypics.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=142.topic&index=104>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.datamagick.com/images/dancing.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: The Fraud</span><hr size=1> &quot;Shhhh Saph. You passed out on us. Kyusz is here to help.&quot; Kaly said. Looking over the Iksar's shoulder, Kaly saw that Stormy hadn't moved one muscle since they came in. She still had a look of shock on her, and her face had drained of color. <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>I wonder what's causing this..? Stormy's been one of the best people persons in Claw..</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> Kaly thought. &quot;Stormy? Maybe sitting down would be a good idea.&quot;<br>
&quot;If you've got this for a moment Ky, I'll go see about Stormy.&quot; <br>
<br>
When Kyusz nodded his assent, Kaly went to where the white haired druidess stood. &quot;Stormy?&quot; At her softly spoken word, Stormygale looked toward Kaly. &quot;Are you ok?&quot; <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.users.bigpond.net.au/tamtam/kalyndria3.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
